divs: Sighting DetailsWas driving home after work at about 9:00 Pm. I saw 3 bright white lights to the East off of Rip Rap Rd just West of were it crosses Fishburg Rd. They were not airplane lights. Nor were they any sort of tower lights. I delayed posting this sighting because I wanted to make sure what I saw wasn't explainable. I know it's not much but maybe someone else saw it.
